# MCP Tool Routing

| Need | Tool |
|---|---|
| JUCE API, CMake plugin options, `dsp::` module | **context7** — library `/websites/juce_master` |
| Ableton/VST3/pluginval/web DSP research | **brave-search** MCP (`brave_web_search`) |
| Multi-step architecture or DSP design reasoning | **thoughtbox** MCP (`thoughtbox_gateway`) |

Read `docs/DSP.md` before tuning audio. Read `docs/BUILD.md` before changing CI.

Do not guess JUCE APIs — query context7 when unsure.
